mapping.kiegel:
contribution >> Contribution > agent*
or
contribution >> Contribution > agent >> agent > rdfs:label

mapping.turtle:
bflc:creatorCharacteristic <value> .
# with literal value
bflc:creatorCharacteristic [ a bflc:CreatorCharacteristic ;
  rdfs:label "value" ] .

_ - propertyLabel: has University of Washington-specific note on work (RDA 5.9)
mapping.kiegel: note >> Note > rdfs:label ; > noteType="University of Washington note"

_ - propertyLabel: work has Library of Congress Geographic Classification
mapping.kiegel: classification >> Classification > rdf:value ; > source >> Source > rdfs:label="Library of Congress Geographic Classification"
